{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1678-07_091","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"Stances à Iris, sur le Prodige de l’Enfant pétrifié","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juillet 1678 [tome 7], p. 91-94.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Vous jugez bien, Madame, que ce qui vient d’arriver à Toulouse a fait d’abord l’entretien de toute la Ville. On ne s’est pas contenté d’en parler. Un fort galant Homme de ce Païs-là en a pris occasion de se plaindre par ces Vers du trop de rigueur d’une belle Dame.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"STANCES À IRIS,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"Sur le Prodige de l’Enfant ","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"pétrifié.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[4]/#"}}]}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Endurcir un tendre Enfant","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans le ventre de sa Mere,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’est pas un Charme si grand","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme on voudroit nous le faire.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’en suis beaucoup moins surpris","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de voir, aimable Iris,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’à vos yeux tout rend les armes,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que s’ils veulent toucher,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces beaux yeux ont mille charmes","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui rendroient tendre un Rocher.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’à jamais puissent les Dieux","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Punir la Vieille cruelle","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui fit les maux en ces lieux","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une Méduse nouvelle !","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’avois longtemps consulté","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourquoy vostre dureté","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’opposoit à ma tendresse,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il faut que pour mon malheur","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un jour cette Enchanteresse","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ait endurcy vostre cœur.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour soulager le tourment","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui me couste tant de larmes,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rompez cet Enchantement,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Opposez Charmes à Charmes.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’abord que vous le voudrez,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Belle Iris, vous le pourrez.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux accords de ma Musete,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cruelle, attendrissez-vous,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le cœur d’une Anaxarete","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sied mal à des yeux si doux.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je le prédis bien un jour,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voyant vostre tyrannie,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que du mépris de l’Amour","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous seriez enfin punie.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cet Enfant des Dieux vainqueur,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’est vangé sur vostre cœur,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des honneurs que luy derobe","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce cœur qui luy fut si cher,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et comme un autre Niobe","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous a changée en Rocher.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous pouvez encore aimer,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si vous faites des conquestes,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et nous sçavez enflamer,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toute Rocher que vous estes.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourrez-vous vous empescher,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fussiez-vous cent fois Rocher,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sensible à mes longs services,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’y répondre quelquefois ?","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Rochers, des Précipices","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Répondent bien à ma voix.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}}]}}}